OL,3,CMan becomes first in England to be
OL,4,Cjailed for cyber-flashing
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Tony Green reports
OL,7,Ffrom Southend-on-sea.
OL,9,FA registered sex offender from
OL,10,FBasildon has become the first person
OL,11,Fin England and Wales to be jailed for
OL,12,Fcyber-flashing, which became an
OL,13,Foffence in January this year.
OL,15,FNicholas Hawkes was sentenced to 66
OL,16,Fweeks behind bars at Southend Crown
OL,17,FCourt for sending unsolicited explicit
OL,18,Fphotos to a 15-year-old girl and a
OL,19,Fwoman.
