OL,3,CMan becomes first in England to be
OL,4,Cjailed for cyber-flashing
OL,6,FNicholas Hawkes, 39, sent photos of
OL,7,Fhis genitals to the girl and woman on
OL,8,F9 February.
OL,10,FThe woman took screenshots of the
OL,11,Fimage on WhatsApp and reported Hawkes
OL,12,Fto Essex Police the same day.
OL,14,FThe case was passed to the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service (CPS) and at a
OL,16,Fremand hearing at Southend
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 12
OL,18,FFebruary, Hawkes pleaded guilty to two
OL,19,Fcounts of sending a photograph or film
OL,20,Fof genitals to cause alarm, distress,
OL,21,For humiliation.
