OL,6,FToday, he pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,7,Fthe order and breaching a suspended
OL,8,Fsentence for another sexual offence.
OL,10,FThe CPS has 4 cases of Cyber-flashing,
OL,11,Fincluding Hawkes', on its books at the
OL,12,Fmoment.
