OL,3,CMan becomes first in England to be
OL,4,Cjailed for cyber-flashing
OL,6,FHannah von Dadelszen, Deputy Chief
OL,7,FCrown Prosecutor for the CPS in the
OL,8,FEast of England, told ITV News this
OL,9,Fsort of behaviour is 'serious' and not
OL,10,Fa joke. She said: "The CPS has in
OL,11,Ftotal 4 cases, including this case, on
OL,12,Fits books at the moment and that is a
OL,13,Fnational picture.
OL,15,F"I hope that the good outcome in this
OL,16,Fcase will encourage more victims to
OL,17,Fcome forward, and encourage them that
OL,18,Ftheir complaints will be taken
OL,19,Fseriously.
