OL,6,F"I think there's a perception that
OL,7,Fthis type of behaviour is a joke and
OL,8,Fthat it is not serious, but this sends
OL,9,Fa very clear signal that it will be
OL,10,Fdealt with in the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem."
