OL,3,CMan becomes first in England to be
OL,4,Cjailed for cyber-flashing
OL,6,F"Hawkes has proven himself to be a
OL,7,Fdangerous individual, and our Crime
OL,8,Fand Public Protection Team have put
OL,9,Fhours of work into ensuring he is
OL,10,Ftaken off the streets.
OL,12,F"Perpetrators may think that by
OL,13,Foffending online, they are less likely
OL,14,Fto be caught, however that is not the
OL,15,Fcase. 'Cyber-flashing' has a
OL,16,Fdetrimental impact on victims, and we
OL,17,Fwill continue to investigate all
OL,18,Freports of this offence.
